ZH: 我在一家大公司实习了一个月。
EN: I interned at a large company for a month.

ZH: 他在医院实习，学到了很多有用的知识。
EN: He interned at a hospital and learned a lot of useful knowledge.

ZH: 实习是为了更好地了解职场。
EN: Internship is to better understand the workplace.

ZH: 我正在寻找暑期实习的机会。
EN: I am looking for summer internship opportunities.

ZH: 实习生需要有很强的学习能力。
EN: Interns need to have strong learning abilities.

ZH: 她通过实习获得了宝贵的工作经验。
EN: She gained valuable work experience through internships.

ZH: 实习生每天都要做很多繁重的工作。
EN: Interns have to do a lot of heavy work every day.

ZH: 实习是学习和工作的结合。
EN: Internship is a combination of learning and working.

ZH: 我的实习结束后，公司发给了我一份证书。
EN: After my internship ended, the company gave me a certificate.

ZH: 实习让我更加熟悉了业务流程。
EN: Internship made me more familiar with the business process.

ZH: 我的实习导师给了我很多指导和帮助。
EN: My internship mentor gave me a lot of guidance and help.

ZH: 实习是一个提升自我能力的好机会。
EN: Internship is a good opportunity to improve self-ability.

ZH: 我的实习生活充实而有意义。
EN: My internship life is fulfilling and meaningful.

ZH: 可以通过实习更好地了解自己的职业规划。
EN: You can better understand your career planning through internships.

ZH: 实习生需要具备团队合作精神。
EN: Interns need to have a spirit of teamwork.

ZH: 每位实习生都要完成一份实习报告。
EN: Each intern has to complete an internship report.

ZH: 实习时间有时候比较辛苦，但是非常值得。
EN: Internship time is sometimes hard, but very worthwhile.

ZH: 实习成功是自己奋斗的结果。
EN: The success of the internship is the result of my own hard work.

ZH: 实习是一段宝贵的人生经历。
EN: Internship is a valuable life experience.
